charges.charge_disposition: It is the jgmt of the crt that the dft shall be comm to the cust of the bop for a term of 33 mos on ea cts of the first superseding indictment, terms to run conc w/each other. Pur to the sent reform act of 1984, it is ord that the dft pay to the U.S. a fine of $3,000. Upon rel from impris the dft shall be placed on supv rel for a term of 3 yrs on each ct, terms of wh shall ron conc under the following terms and cond. (1) the dft shall comply w/r&;r of the po and go 318, (2) the dft shall pay any fine imp by this jgmt that remains unpaid at the commencement of supv rel, as dir by the po, (3) as dir by the po, the dft shall notify 3rd parties of risks by the dft's criminal rec or personal history, (4) the dft is prohibited from ownin g or dealing in firearms and or explosive devices, as well as any employment involving the same. It is fur ord, the dft shall pay a s/a of $100.00 to the U.S. Crt adopts the justification of the po. Dft informed of right to appeal and dft comm t o the cust f/w commitment no. 1292 prepared.
